&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1">// 리뷰어 제안: &amp;#34;타임아웃 설정이 필요할 것 같아요.&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
